<h3 id="the-ruby-gems">The Ruby Gems</h3>

<p>Ruby on Rails has the biggest community and daily basis pushing new gem to eliminate the repeating. following are some of the gems I often find useful and mostly use in each and every project.</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/plataformatec/devise">Devise</a> Anything to do with Auth</li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/plataformatec/simple_form">Simple Form</a> To build forms</li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/indirect/haml-rails">HAML</a> HTML is boring, so I use HAML</li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/carrierwaveuploader/carrierwave">CarrierWave</a> To upload anything anywhere</li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/prawnpdf/prawn">Prawn</a> PDF generation</li>
</ul>

